Salter vs. State. Keeping open Tipling Houses on Sunday, from City Court op Savannah. Criminal Law. Charge of Court. (Before Judge Harden.) Garrard & Meldrim, for plaintiff in error. F. G. DuBignon, solicitor'general, by brief, for the State.

[Jáckson, C. J., not presiding, because of indisposition.]

Blandford, J.

This case is controlled by the preceding case of Seiler us. State.

Judgment affirmed.
